OL,3,CWhat does decriminalising cannabis
OL,4,Cmean and how would it work in Jersey?
OL,6,FPossessing, selling and buying
OL,7,Fcannabis is illegal. However, the
OL,8,FStates recently voted for repeat
OL,9,Foffenders with small amounts for
OL,10,Fpersonal use to be sent to their
OL,11,Fparish hall to be dealt with, rather
OL,12,Fthan going through the courts.
