OL,3,CWhat does decriminalising cannabis
OL,4,Cmean and how would it work in Jersey?
OL,6,FDecriminalising cannabis for personal
OL,7,Fuse is not the same as legalisation.
OL,8,FIt means that people found with small
OL,9,Famounts for themselves would not be
OL,10,Fcharged by the police. However,
OL,11,Fcannabis would still be illegal and
OL,12,Fplaces would not be allowed to sell it.
