OL,3,CWhat does decriminalising cannabis
OL,4,Cmean and how would it work in Jersey?
OL,6,FDeputy Tom Coles may be able to count
OL,7,Fon the support of Health Minister Tom
OL,8,FBinet who has been quoted as saying a
OL,9,Fsofter stance "would make a lot of
OL,10,Fsense".
OL,12,FChief Minister Lyndon Farnham also
OL,13,Fsaid he would not be against it,
OL,14,Fprovided there is enough evidence to
OL,15,Fsupport the move.
OL,17,FJersey is further down the road than
OL,18,FGuernsey but it is still early days
OL,19,Fand other politicians are opposed to
OL,20,Fany changes in the law.
